programme.title: A Good Man
programme.desc: Efter att en lysande karriar inom en militar specialstyrka slutar i katastrof, drar sig Alexander (Seagal) undan rampljuset och forsoker leva ett lugnt liv som hantverkare i ett lagenhetskomplex i Rumanien.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Udda eller jamt
programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Sightings
programme.desc: Ett science fiction-mysterium om en dysfunktionell familj som bor på en ranch i Texas och hotas av en varelse i skogen. For att kunna overleva hotet måste de samtidigt losa sina egna inre konflikter.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Fungi
programme.desc: Ett fartfyllt aventyr som staller vetenskap och naturlig balans mot kortsiktigt tankande i en kamp for mansklighetens overlevnad.

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond står infor ett vagskal i livet. Han har nyligen separerat från sin fru och blir ombedd att ta hand om deras son Leo over helgen. Illa tajmat då han just ar i fard med att iscensatta en konstkupp for lite snabba pengar. Leo ar helt ovetandes om planen och bara ser fram emot att får spendera tid med sin efterlangtade pappa. Tatt inpå kommer verkligheten snabbt ikapp Charlie som nu ar i allra hogsta grad en jagad man av skoningslosa torpeder. Hans enda hopp ar att lyckats fly ut ur landet och att få återstalla sin relation till Leo som han vanskott i alla år.

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Dragon Lord
programme.desc: Dragon och Bull fordriver tiden mestadels med att glida omkring och jaga tjejer. Speciellt en, som Dragon ar sarskilt fortjust i. Efter ett misslyckat forsok att skicka ett karleksbrev hamnar radarparet ovantat på taket till en kriminellt gangs hogkvarter. Ganget stjal dyrbara artefakter från stadens tempel for att smuggla vidare till giriga vasterlanningar, men Dragon och Bull kanner for forsta gången sin plikt, och bestammer sig for att ta sig an ganget.

programme.title: Saknad i strid (Missing in Action)
programme.desc: Amerikanska soldater hålls fångna i Vietnam — och det ar upp till en man att fora hem dem i denna fartfyllda action/aventyrsfilm med kampsportslegenden Chuck Norris. Efter en djarv flykt från ett krigsfånglager ar overste James Braddock (Norris) på ett uppdrag att lokalisera och radda saknade soldater med hjalp av en tjansteman från utrikesdepartementet (Lenore Kasdorf) och en tidigare armekompis (M. Emmet Walsh). Denna enmansarme ar redo att ta sig in i Vietnam… men kan han ta sig ut igen?

programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Miami Supercops
programme.desc: Har kommer annu en actionspackad komedi från den dynamiska duon Hill och Spencer. I "Miami Supercops" ser vi våra hjaltar jaga både brottslingar och 20 miljoner dollar som stals vid ett rån for ett par år sedan. Vi får uppleva mord, forodelse och totalt kaos under deras jakt på bytet och rånarna - och naturligtvis får de hjalp av två snygga tjejer!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Elektra
programme.desc: Marvels femme fatale; Elektra (Garner) bevisar att utseende kan doda nar den sexigaste actionhjalten någonsin bryter sig ut från serietidningssidorna till filmduken. I sitt nya uppdrag tvingas hon fatta ett odesdigert beslut i kampen mellan gott och ont!

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Jumper
programme.desc: Av regissoren till The Bourne Identity kommer annu en extrem adrenalinchock som tanjer på fantasins begransningar… David Rice ar en ung man utan granser – en “jumper” – fodd med den markliga formågan att kunna teleportera sig sjalv vart som helst på jorden inom ett ogonblick. Nar David upptacker att det finns fler som honom sjalv kastas han plotsligt in mitt i ett forntida krig. Han jagas av en blodtorstig skara fanatiker, fast beslutna att utrota alla jumpers. Nu måste David anvanda sin mycket speciella gåva smart for att ha en chans att overleva…

programme.title: Ghost Rider - Spirit Of Vengeance
programme.desc: Eld ska med eld bekampas! Johnny Blaze kampar alltjamt mot sin forbannelse som djavulens prisjagare. Och nar en hemlig religios sekt vill anlita hans tjanster, kanner han sig inte redo att annu en gång iklada sig Ghost Riders brinnande krafter och makt. Men kanske ar detta den sista mojligheten att gora sig fri från djavulens forbannelse en gång for alla!

programme.title: Instrument of War
programme.desc: Den amerikanska piloten Clair Cline blir nedskjuten och hamnar i fångenskap i norra Tyskland. En kamp tar slut, en annan tar vid – att hålla hoppet vid liv trots taggtråd och fortryck. Cline och hans medfångar måste hitta ett satt att hålla ihop, inte bara for att overleva utan aven for att utharda fångenskapen. Baserad på sanna handelser.

programme.title: Survivor
programme.desc: Survivor ar en thriller om en av det amerikanska utrikesdepartementets sakerhetsexperter som får en tjanst vid USA:s ambassad i London. Hennes jobb ar att stoppa terrorister från att ta sig in i USA och det placerar henne direkt i skottlinjen. Dodshotad, oskyldigt brottsanklagad, vanhedrad och på flykt måste hon till varje pris komma på hur hon ska rentvå sig och samtidigt stoppa en omfattande terrorattack som ar planerad att aga rum under nyårsfirandet vid Times Square i New York.

programme.title: Blood And Bone
programme.desc: Isaiah Bone (Michael Jai White) ar en skicklig mastare i kampsport. Efter fem år bakom galler skall han nu ut i verkligheten och borja ett nytt liv. Han anlander till Los Angeles dar ingen vet vem han ar och dar overraskar han alla genom att slåss som en varldsmastare. På gatorna i LA ar det gangsterkungen James som styr och Bone tar sig snart an utmaningen att forsoka storta honom. Men Bone doljer en mork hemlighet och han ar dessutom ute efter hamnd. Bone upptacker snart att han måste slåss for sitt liv. Allt står på spel! EN VISUELLT BLÄNDANDE ACTIONFILM MED MICHAEL JAI WHITE (’Spawn’), JULIAN SANDS (’24 timmar’) OCH NONA GAYE (’Matrix Reloaded’).

programme.title: Dangerous Man
programme.desc: Efter 15 år bakom galler ar oskyldigt domde Shane Daniels åter en fri man. Men nar han blir vittne till en blodig uppgorelse dar den ryska maffian ar inblandad, kastas Shane in i ett brutalt gisslandrama. Med den nyvunna friheten som insats måste han kampa mot skrupulosa gangstrar for att radda en oskyldig flickas liv...

programme.title: Texas Killing Fields
programme.desc: Mellan 1983 och 1991 hittas fyra kvinnokroppar på samma plats i en stad i Texas. The Fields ar den sanna historien om en mans trettioåriga kamp for att losa mordgåtan, i det forgiftade oljelandskapet som kallas for Killing Fields.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Americas National Parks - Grand Canyon
programme.desc: The Grand Canyon is a steep-sided canyon carved by the Colorado River in Arizona, United States. The Grand Canyon is 277 miles (446 km) long, up to 18 miles (29 km) wide and attains a depth of over a mile (6,093 feet or 1,857 meters). The canyon and adjacent rim are contained within Grand Canyon National Park, the Kaibab National Forest, Grand Canyon–Parashant National Monument, the Hualapai Indian Reservation, the Havasupai Indian Reservation and the Navajo Nation. President Theodore Roosevelt was a major proponent of preservation of the Grand Canyon area and visited it on numerous occasions to hunt and enjoy the scenery.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Of Flying Foxes and Heat Waves
programme.desc: While the Tolga Bat Hospital is looking after endangered flying foxes, researchers are using thermographic cameras to search for flying foxes and koalas. But they can also detect bush and wildfire more quickly.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Of Sea Turtles and Coral Reefs
programme.desc: The Cairns Turtle Rehabilitation Center (CTRC) raises and cares for sick, or injured turtles, while the Schmidt Ocean Institute goes on a diving mission with a high-tech underwater rover. In this way, we learn firsthand about the state of Australias sensitive marine animals natural habitat and what needs to be done to ensure their survival.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Of Wombats and Vaccines
programme.desc: Tasmanias Bonorong Wildlife Sanctuary used to be a traditional wildlife park - now it is an innovative and active wildlife sanctuary and home to the famous Tasmanian Devil, to wombats, and many other native species. But unfortunately, "Tassie Devils" are particularly endangered by the Devil Facial Tumor Disease (DFTD). We accompany the team of young, ambitious scientists on their fight against the disease.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Of Koalas and Drones
programme.desc: Lone Pine Koala Sanctuary was opened in 1927 at a time when Koalas were still being killed on a large scale for the fur trade. Today, hardly anything threatens the natural habitats of these animals as much as the desertification of the forests. We let the drones fly and are there when a new tree is planted.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 wOf Kangaroos and Conservation
programme.desc: Visiting the fenced nature reserve Arid Recovery in southern Australia, we witness the care of an injured kangaroo and follow researchers at the Hidden Vale Wildlife Centre near Brisbane as they train native animals to detect tracks of threatening predators and then move to safety.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Of Fairy Penguins and GPS Trackers
programme.desc: Australias largest fur seal colony is located on Phillip Island. Night after night, a breathtaking spectacle takes place here: At sunset, countless fairy penguins return from their hunt for fish. In the station near the penguin colony, pioneering scientific research is conducted around the cute animals. We learn how dedicated scientists are trying to secure the future of the fairy penguins with the help of GPS trackers.

programme.title: Symphony of the Seas - Underwater Wonders of Australias Ocean
programme.desc: Our journeys take us all around the world from Patagonia to the USA, from Greenland to South Africa and from Cambodia to Australia and leads us to the most fascinating places where landscapes animals and humans are the main focus of our documentaries. Whether on land or at sea – the last paradises of the world are our destination.

programme.title: Jacques Cousteaus Legacy - Return To The Undersea World
programme.desc: A composition of wildlife footage, archive material and elaborate re-enactments results in a brilliant reconstruction of the life of famed marine biologist and environmental pioneer Jacques Cousteau. On the trail of the most famous oceanographer of the 20th Century, the team spent two years filming original locations on three different continents, in four different oceans. The film charts how Cousteau’s outlook on the environment changed throughout his many decades at sea around the globe. On his personal journey to enlightenment, he changed from a man who killed sharks in hate and thoughtlessly blew up coral reefs, to a radical environmentalist.

programme.title: Red Panda - Worlds Cutest Animal
programme.desc: The Red Panda is undoubtedly one of the most beautiful animals on earth and this is the first ever intimate portrait ever made.

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: In a land of dangers, plant-eating animals are always at risk, and never more so than at the time of their birth; out on the open they are vulnerable and there are few places to hide. But luckily some are born to run …

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: Its a water world and life couldnt survive without it. And thanks to it, a mind blowing diversity of creatures thrive beneath the surface. Born to enjoy the riches underwater they must master their bodys adaptations, learn to find food, to escape danger and above all become expert swimmers! Whether its in rivers, on beaches or in the deep ocean, all must overcome the obstacles and fulfil their destiny, all are born to swim! Of all the habitats on earth, the ocean is perhaps the most challenging. Here salt, temperatures, currents and predators can make life difficult; its not an obvious place to want to bring up your babies… But even in these waters generation after generation beats...

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: Baby animals beguile with their innocent charm. But while some remain harmless, others have a deep-rooted instinct. It may take weeks or months of training to hone their skills. Their landscapes and lifestyles maybe very different, but these babies are born to hunt.

programme.title: Wild Medicine - Animals Superpowers
programme.desc: Nature has many weird creatures to offer and often these animals fascinate us the most. There are ants in Australias outback that use specialised workers as living honey pots. In Africa in the endless Bangweulu wetlands of Zambia the shoebill is on the hunt for fish, a bird that definitely lives up to its name. Finally in the Brazilian rainforests lurk gruesome river monsters in the Amazon abyss that send shivers down the spine of even the most experienced divers. But there are also intense human-animal-relationships like the close bond between a German diver and a dolphin female who explore the Atlantic off the coast of Ireland, or the "easy rider" in California who has taken care of an...

programme.title: Unusual World
programme.desc: The dominance of air has always been in the mind of men, but nature only gave the gift to flight to certain animals. Amongst these, to the insects. Thanks to their wings, the insects have conquered most parts of the planet’s diverse environment. What are the reasons for such an amazing biological success without comparison in the history of the animal world?

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Kinabatangan River: Borneo – Forgotten Paradise
programme.desc: In Sabah, northern Borneo, flows the 560km-long Kinabatangan River. Nowhere else in Sabah are wild animals as easily spotted as along this river: orangutans, elephants, crocodiles, and proboscis monkeys. However, biodiversity is threatened as more rainforest gives way to palm oil plantations. Wildlife ventures into inhabited areas in search of food, leading to conflicts. Locals are fighting to preserve the rainforest and its unique wildlife, demonstrating that conservation and prosperity can coexist even in a modern society.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Pu Mat National Park: Vietnam – Of Bears and Men
programme.desc: The jungle in northern Vietnam is nearly impenetrable, with some areas never touched by humans. The remote rainforests of Pu Mat National Park serve as a refuge for endangered wildlife such as black bears, monkeys, and pangolins. Tuan, a biologist and bear specialist, embarks on an expedition to these untouched regions of the park in search of bears. The most hunted animal here is the pangolin, sought after for its scales believed to have medicinal properties and its meat considered a delicacy. A small Vietnamese conservation organization fights for the survival of this species.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Gaoligongshan Park: China – Himalaya’s Gold
programme.desc: The Great Gobi National Park in southwestern Mongolia shelters one of the last populations of wild Bactrian camels, amid its ancient and mysterious desert landscape. With around 800 critically endangered animals, the Gobi remains one of the worlds most sparsely inhabited and inhospitable regions, yet its allure is undeniable, offering a captivating backdrop for encounters with wild camels and stories of people deeply connected to nature.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Great Gobi National Park: Mongolia – Following the Wild Camels
programme.desc: The jungle in northern Vietnam is nearly impenetrable, with some areas never touched by humans. programme.title: Faroe Islands - A Secret Beauty
programme.desc: The Faroe Islands in the North Atlantic, located in the middle of the Gulf Stream between Scotland and Iceland, are an archipelago of eighteen green volcanic islands where a unique culture has developed over the last thousand years. As direct descendants of the Vikings, the Faroese feel committed to their traditions and hold on to customs, without missing out on the advantages of the modern and globalised world - from archaic hunter and shepherd culture to contemporary art. With the highest birth rate in Europe and the lowest social inequality in the world, the just fifty thousand Faroese are a very special people living on one of the last natural paradises in Europe.

programme.title: mareTV: The white wilderness in Greenlands East
programme.desc: Fjords, glaciers and the highest mountains in the Arctic: East Greenland with its spectacular nature is one of the most sparsely populated regions on earth. The people here live in extreme isolation and depend on helicopter flights for their supplies. Despite harsh conditions, the inhabitants here lovingly maintain their traditions and enjoy their outdoor leisure time even at minus 20 degrees Celsius. The town of Tasiilaq is the "metropolis" with 4,000 inhabitants and offers a very special attraction: the only ski lift on the east coast. Thomas Mikaelsen, the lift attendant, is not to be envied for his job. The only 100 meter long lift comes from Switzerland and is already 20 years old....

programme.title: Magical Moors
programme.desc: Wide open heaths, windswept and barren in winter, are transformed into wonderful carpets of white, fluffy cotton grass in summer. Large bears and wolves roam alongside delicately fluttering butterflies, the bubbling calls of black grouse and the enchanting trills of the great snipe. Moors, bogs and wetlands can be found all over in Europe. Everyone has at least heard about this habitat but most know little about it. It is an ancient yet largely unknown set of landscapes that is full of enchanting surprises. On a warm spring day, poisonous adders emerge from hiding to perform their impressive mating dance. As dusk falls, snipe gather on traditional leks, leaping and singing to impress the...

programme.title: The Sudheide - Woods, meadows, open country
programme.desc: Forests and fields, moors and heathland, shepherds and sheep - these are the symbols of an ostensibly unspoilt landscape that has inspired poets and painters alike for centuries. The secret of the almost 500 km² nature reserve Naturpark Sudheide lies in its diversity: the origins of its soil, geology and topography can be traced back to the ice age. But the region between Hamburg and Hannover is anything but unspoilt. For centuries, it was synonymous with heathland farmers and formed as a North German cultivated landscape. This documentary tells of an almost unknown region, which has been strongly influenced by mankind for centuries, yet still remains diverse in its nature. Nature...

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wild Life, Gentle Nature
programme.desc: As contrasting as the landscapes of the 15th meridian east, so different are its animal inhabitants. What are the living conditions like in the heat of the Namibian Damaraland, in Lusatia or on the coast of Norway? Which challenges do elephants, whales or kingfishers have to master together with their companions from north to south?

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.desc: Almost 11000 kilometres lie between the northernmost and southernmost point of the 15th meridian east. Here you will find extreme landscapes such as the shimmering heat of Africa or the eternal cold of northern Scandinavia. Five people from Spitsbergen, Namibia, Slovenia, Germany and Poland dedicate their lives to environmental protection.

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Sow, Harvest, Eat – Our Conservatory
programme.desc: This episode focuses on people from five countries who share a common passion: The production of their own food and food. What culinary treasures are hidden in the different regions, from Spitsbergen to Sweden, Austria, Poland and Chad?

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 From Generation to Generation
programme.desc: The journey leads from the Norwegian Vesterålen to Chad, the Aeolian Islands and the Polish Giant Mountains. As different as the landscapes and cultures may be, all people are united in their love for their children and their desire to give something to tomorrows generation.

programme.title: 15th Meridian East - Similarity in Difference
programme.desc: What ideas are people on the 15th meridian east developing to shape the future and leave tomorrows generations a home worth living in? This consequence leads us to four future designers. From the barren Namib Desert to the glacier worlds of Spitsbergen, Sicily and the Croatian Mediterranean.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Gir National Park: India – Asia’s Last Lion
programme.desc: In the far west of India, unexpected predators roam: lions. Living freely in a human-inhabited area without fences, they occasionally prey on the livestock of the indigenous Maldhari people, who nevertheless take pride in sharing their region with these lions—a unique coexistence of humans and predators. In northern Gujarat, desert landscapes dominate, where semi-nomadic communities breed a unique camel breed capable of swimming: Karai camels swim up to 3km daily to mangrove islands for grazing.

programme.title: King of the Mountains - Golden Eagle
programme.desc: Aerial shots of mating Golden eagles, a clash between a Golden and a White-tailed eagle, and an intimate glimpse into their nesting grounds combine to create a spectacular film. Tracking these majestic birds reveals the wild nature of their hunting grounds, showcasing the diverse animal and plant life that share their habitat with the king of the skies. Viewers are brought up close as the eagle effortlessly glides over forests and canyons, abruptly diving in a breathtaking pursuit of prey. Witnessing these birds in their natural habitats is witnessing them at their finest. Embark on a magnificent journey through the skies and landscapes with us.

programme.title: King of the Seas - Sea Eagle
programme.desc: The times where eagles have been seen as varmints are over. They are now perceived as an integral part of the food cycle. Due to the fact that the habitats of the sea eagles in Germany are largely found in the north-eastern regions that are rich in water, the movie accompanies the eagles to an island, home to hundreds of sea ravens, where they rob the baby sea ravens of their food. They seem to always profit from the successes of the fellow creatures in their habitats. This film introduces you to the expert poachers of the animal kingdom.

programme.title: Leap Of The Lynx
programme.desc: On the Iberian Peninsula, primeval landscapes are practically non-existent, so the Iberian lynx has lived on cultivated land for centuries – cattle, horse and pig pastures, cork oak forests, timberland, and even holy sites of pilgrimage. The diversity and beauty of these locations are truly stunning and their character and history as relevant to this story as that of the big cat itself. Until five years ago, both populations of Iberian lynx were quickly fading away. Their fragmented habitats were shrinking even further, they were starved by lack of prey and reduced by epidemics. But now, local authorities, scientists, landowners, and other groups have finally begun to act in unison.

programme.title: Notorious Criminals
programme.desc: With his Subway diet, Jared Fogle became an inspiration but his wholesome exterior wasnt all that it was cracked up to be as he led the secret life of a sexual predator and amassed charges of child pornography and pedophilia.

programme.title: US Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: Benny is in bar keeping a close eye on his drunk defendant until the rest of the Bounty hunters arrive...and when they do arrive all hell breaks loose.

programme.title: US Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: The Bounty Hunters are shocked that their cuffed defendant manages to slip out of the car and take off.

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime
programme.desc: In 1986, an American becomes one of Canadas most prolific bank and jewellery bandits after he pulls off one of the biggest heists in Canadian history.

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime
programme.desc: In 1994, a troubled single mother is found raped and murdered in her apartment.

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.title: The Permian
programme.desc: Massive geologic changes allowed life to thrive on land and sea, producing saber-toothed carnivores like Gorgonopsid and the terrifying 40-foot shark Helicoprion.

programme.title: The Triassic
programme.desc: After the Permian period, the epic saga of evolution and extinction on Earth produced the worlds first dinosaurs, plesiosaurs and pterosaurs.

programme.title: The Cretaceous
programme.desc: Magnificent and terrifying dinosaurs like Triceratops and Tyrannosaurus ruled the land. But they were all wiped out in an instant by a collision with an asteroid!

programme.title: The Ordovician
programme.desc: For nearly 4 billion years, the continents of Earth were lifeless. But during the Ordovician, there was an explosion of life beneath the sea. Many creatures evolved.

programme.title: The Devonian
programme.desc: Life in the sea rebounded with a vengeance in the Devonian. Dozens of monstrous predators emerged, like the 40-foot long Dunkleosteus.

programme.title: Alien Life
programme.desc: Scientists investigate microbes found in Yellowstone National Parks thermal pools to understand the biology necessary for life at high temperatures.

programme.title: Frozen Archeology
programme.desc: There are places in Greater Yellowstone where the snow never melts, or at least, it never used to. Climate change is causing Yellowstone’s ice patches to recede.

programme.title: The Petrified Forest
programme.desc: Greater Yellowstone sits on top of a volcanic hot spot where devastating geological events unfolded. The result? A bizarre cemetery of fossilized forests.

programme.title: Mammoth Country
programme.desc: The Greater Yellowstone Area was once a rich grazing ground for huge Columbian mammoths. Now it’s a prime hunting ground for paleontologists and archaeologists.

programme.title: The Last Triceratops
programme.desc: Montana’s Hell Creek Formation is home to a trove of late Cretaceous fossils unlike any other in the world, revealing the last days of the great dinosaurs.

programme.title: Past and Future Yellowstone
programme.desc: Craters of the Moon National Monument is desolate – but 2,200 years ago, it was the site of today’s Yellowstone Hotspot, known for violent eruptions and huge craters.

programme.title: Worlds Best Dinosaur Fossil
programme.desc: An extraordinary new discovery of a dinosaur fossil so pristine and complete, that it shows off the texture, patterns, and color of a prehistoric giant. Discover this brand new species that roamed during the late Jurassic and Cretaceous periods.

programme.title: Recovering From Extinction
programme.desc: How long does it take for life to rebound after a major mass extinction? Scientists in Svalbard dig through fossil clues for surprising revelations about our Earths history.

programme.title: T-Rex Timeline
programme.desc: The Tyrannosaurus Rex is known as the king of the dinosaurs, but how did its reign begin? Meet Moros Intrepidus, a 180 lb., deer-sized ancestor to the T-Rex.

programme.title: Raising Dinos From The Dead
programme.desc: Could a 75 million-year-old dinosaur skull that has been sitting in a museum for over 20 years hold the first-ever dinosaur DNA discovered by humans?

programme.title: The Rise and Fall Of T-Rex
programme.desc: T-rex - the "tyrant lizard king" - ruled the earth 65 million years ago. Today, he reigns as the ultimate predator and pop cultural icon.

programme.title: The Permian
programme.desc: Massive geologic changes allowed life to thrive on land and sea, producing saber-toothed carnivores like Gorgonopsid and the terrifying 40-foot shark Helicoprion.

programme.title: The Triassic
programme.desc: After the Permian period, the epic saga of evolution and extinction on Earth produced the worlds first dinosaurs, plesiosaurs and pterosaurs.

programme.title: The Cretaceous
programme.desc: Magnificent and terrifying dinosaurs like Triceratops and Tyrannosaurus ruled the land. But they were all wiped out in an instant by a collision with an asteroid!

programme.title: The Ordovician
programme.desc: For nearly 4 billion years, the continents of Earth were lifeless. But during the Ordovician, there was an explosion of life beneath the sea. Many creatures evolved.

programme.title: The Devonian
programme.desc: Life in the sea rebounded with a vengeance in the Devonian. Dozens of monstrous predators emerged, like the 40-foot long Dunkleosteus.

programme.title: Alien Life
programme.desc: Scientists investigate microbes found in Yellowstone National Parks thermal pools to understand the biology necessary for life at high temperatures.

programme.title: Frozen Archeology
programme.desc: There are places in Greater Yellowstone where the snow never melts, or at least, it never used to. Climate change is causing Yellowstone’s ice patches to recede.

programme.title: The Petrified Forest
programme.desc: Greater Yellowstone sits on top of a volcanic hot spot where devastating geological events unfolded. The result? A bizarre cemetery of fossilized forests.

programme.title: Mammoth Country
programme.desc: The Greater Yellowstone Area was once a rich grazing ground for huge Columbian mammoths. Now it’s a prime hunting ground for paleontologists and archaeologists.

programme.title: The Last Triceratops
programme.desc: Montana’s Hell Creek Formation is home to a trove of late Cretaceous fossils unlike any other in the world, revealing the last days of the great dinosaurs.

programme.title: Part 1: Rise of Civilization
programme.desc: In the region that includes the Mediterranean, the Aegean, Mesopotamia and Egypt, the Bronze Age arrived about 3000 BC and lasted nearly 2000 years. What singled out this period and the new societies and cities that emerged? The development of formal writing is one among several important factors.

programme.title: Part 2: Masters Of Trade
programme.desc: Trade, and in particular trade in luxury goods, drove the commerce economies of the Bronze Age. This is the time when the first super powers in history, Egypt and Mesopotamia, emerge and dominate the "world" stage of the Mediterranean and Aegean seas and surrounding areas.

programme.title: Part 3: Conquest And Collapse
programme.desc: The Bronze Age had the first large urban centers, powerful kingdoms and armies, writing, and trade routes across vast areas. What led to the collapse of the city-state entities and the end of the Bronze Age? Possibly a perfect storm of uncontrollable factors that are still being researched.

programme.title: Pierce Arrow
programme.desc: 1913 38C Brougham - "built up to a standard, not down to a price" - was worth the value of several houses at the time, with the special cachet of being the first car owned by the White House.

programme.title: Duesenberg
programme.desc: The 1930 Model J Duesenberg was the pinnacle of automotive engineering in power and speed, holding records not surpassed until the 1960s.

programme.title: Terraplane
programme.desc: The Hudson Terraplane 1937 Series 72 was a fast and affordable car with unique style and innovative design. The company, unlike others, survived the Depression.

programme.title: Corvette
programme.desc: The 1963 Split-Window Stingray Coupe combined power, performance, precision and youthful design.

programme.title: Oldsmobile
programme.desc: The Oldsmobile F88 was a "dream car" of the GM Oldsmobile line, but the auto, despite its sophisticated, debonair styling, was destined never to see production.

programme.title: Mustang
programme.desc: The Ford Mustang Shelby GT-500 was born of the 1960s vibe and the racing experience of Carroll Shelby, who set speed records at Bonnevile salt flats.

programme.title: The Hunt for the Slave Ship Guerrero
programme.desc: A team of underwater archeologists searches for the remains of the Guerrero, an illegal slave ship sunk in battle off the coast of Florida.

programme.title: The Last Persian Shah
programme.desc: Shah Mohammad Reza Pahlavi would have been 100 years in October 2019. The Shahs story begins with good ideas and ideals and ends in bloody chaos.

programme.title: Radioactive Forest - 10 Years After
programme.desc: We look at the satoyama landscape ten years after the nuclear disaster at Fukushima Daiichi Power Plant which was followed by the 3.11 megaquake.

programme.title: The Greatest
programme.desc: Allen och Grace Brewer har forlorat sin aldsta son i en bilolycka, nar det plotsligt ringerpå dorren. Utanfor står Rose. Hon sager att hon kande deras son. Och att hon vantar hans barn. Forst får det familjen att falla isar ytterligare. Men kanske kan avenden svåraste olycka leda till ny lycka?

programme.title: Danny Collins
programme.desc: Al Pacino spelar 1970-talsrockaren Danny Collins som fortfarande lever hårt for att do ung. Nar hans manager hittar ett brev som John Lennon 40 år tidigare skrev till Danny, ett brev som han aldrig har last, så bestammer han sig for att byta kurs. Han ger sig ut på en gripande resa for att hitta tillbaka till sin familj, hitta den sanna karleken och påborja nasta akt i livet. Det fantastiska soundtracket innehåller låtar av John Lennon.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Runaway Jury
programme.desc: Från mastaren John Grisham kommer en thriller med Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, John Cusack och Rachel Weisz. En jury-fixare spelar ett dodligt katt-och-råtta-spel med en jurymedlem och en mystisk framling som båda erbjuder att "leverera" domen till hogstbjudande. Snart står både liv och miljoner på spel i en pulshojare full av ovantade vandningar.

programme.title: Birdman
programme.desc: I den omtalade och kritikerhyllade svarta komedin BIRDMAN eller The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance ser vi Michael Keaton i huvudrollen som en skådespelare, mest kand for att ha spelat den ikoniska superhjalten Birdman. Han ska nu regissera en teateruppforestallning på Broadway och vi får folja honom under de hektiska dagarna innan den stora premiarkvallen. Samtidigt som han slåss mot sina inre demoner och sitt stora ego så forsoker han lappa ihop både familj och karriar. For regi står Alejandro G. Iñárritu (BABEL, ÄLSKADE HUNDAR) och i ovriga roller ser vi bl.a. Zach Galifianakis, Edward Norton, Emma Stone, Naomi Watts.

programme.title: K-19: The Widowmaker
programme.desc: 1961 inleder Sovjetunionens forsta karnvapenbarande ubåt på sin jungfruresa i Nordatlanten. Men ubåten fungerar inte optimalt, och når det uppstår fel med karnreaktorn har den katastrofala konsekvenser for besattningen. Tillsammans måste besattningen kampa for att undvika en karnkatastrof som både ar livshotande och kan starta ett nytt varldskrig mellan de två supermakterna.

programme.title: Auggie
programme.desc: Felix Greystone har en bit kvar till pensionsåldern, men foretaget pressar honom att gå i fortidspension. I avskedsgåva får han ett par smartglasogon, som vacker anvandarens storsta drommar till liv. Nar Felix frus karriar tar fart och dottern borjar bli sjalvstandig inser Felix hur ensam han kanner sig. For att fly den plågsamma ensamheten fordjupar Felix sig allt mer i sina smartglasogons varld, vilket påfrestar Felix relation till familjen ytterligare.

programme.title: Main Street
programme.desc: Romantiken och hoppet spirar nar en karismatisk framling anlander till den borttynande lilla staden. Med sig har han ett erbjudande som vander upp och ned på tillvaron for invånarna - och inget kommer någonsin att bli sig likt igen. Ett stjarnspackat drama om livet och karleken med en strålande Colin Firth i huvudrollen.

programme.title: Son of the South
programme.desc: Verklig historia om en KKK-medlems barnbarn som vaxer upp i borjan av 1960-talet. Trots att han fostrats in i hatet intresserar han sig for medborgarrattsrorelsen.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Danny Collins
programme.desc: Al Pacino spelar 1970-talsrockaren Danny Collins som fortfarande lever hårt for att do ung. Nar hans manager hittar ett brev som John Lennon 40 år tidigare skrev till Danny, ett brev som han aldrig har last, så bestammer han sig for att byta kurs. Han ger sig ut på en gripande resa for att hitta tillbaka till sin familj, hitta den sanna karleken och påborja nasta akt i livet. Det fantastiska soundtracket innehåller låtar av John Lennon.

programme.title: Brother
programme.desc: Gangstern Yamamoto tvingas i exil av sin Yakuza, och styr kosan mot Los Angeles for att leta efter sin halvbror Ken.

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Palo Alto
programme.desc: High School-eleverna Teddy, April, Fred och Emily ar som alla andra på jakt efter något att gora i Palo Altos tråkiga forortsmiljo. April ar vilsen och dras mellan en attraktion till sin aldre fotbollstranare och en oskuldsfull foralskelse i Teddy – en strulig skejtare vars kompis Fred bojar tappa greppet. Den lika vilsna Emily anvander istallet sex for att få bekraftelse.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Dont Come Knocking
programme.desc: Hollywoodstjarnan Howard Spence (Sam Shepard) har sett battre dagar. Han vilar på sina lagrar och lever på sin gamla stjarnstatus. Efter ytterligare en natt med vilda utsvavningar flyr han från inspelningen av nasta vasternfilm och rider ut på prarien och de stora vidderna precis som en av hjaltarna som han så ofta har gestaltat. Han soker tillflykt hemma hos sin mamma (Eva Marie Saint) som han inte har traffat på många år. Men inte ens dar stannar han sarskilt lange, for han får veta att han någonstans kan ha en son som han inte visste fanns. For Howard kanns det som en strimma hopp och ett bevis for att inte har levt sitt liv forgaves.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: Proxima
programme.desc: Sarah ar en fransk astronaut, och den enda kvinnliga deltagaren i det rymdprogram som forbereder sig infor en ett år lång expedition. Som ensamstående mamma till en åttaåring kanns expeditionen an mer kravande, och med lika delar skuld och mod forsoker hon hitta balans i sin roll som banbrytare och mamma.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Runaway Jury
programme.desc: Från mastaren John Grisham kommer en thriller med Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, John Cusack och Rachel Weisz. En jury-fixare spelar ett dodligt katt-och-råtta-spel med en jurymedlem och en mystisk framling som båda erbjuder att "leverera" domen till hogstbjudande. Snart står både liv och miljoner på spel i en pulshojare full av ovantade vandningar.

programme.title: Jimmy P.
programme.desc: En orolig indianveteran bildar en exceptionell vanskap med en fransk psykoanalytiker nar de forsoker hitta botemedel mot deras lidande.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. De två sprintertjejerna kampar for att kvala in till VM i friidrott och moter tuffa motgångar och bitter rivalitet på sin dramatiska, hjartevarmande och inspirerande resa.

programme.title: Man on Fire
programme.desc: MAN ON FIRE ar en gripande thriller med Oscar® belonade Denzel Washington i huvudrollen. Han spelar Creasy, en f.d. utbrand CIA agent som tappat livsgnistan. Creasy overtalas av sin van Rayburn (Christopher Walken) att skydda en tioårig flicka i Mexico City dar barnkidnappningar tillhor vardagen. Creasy kommer flickan nara och deras relation gor att han återfår viljan att leva. Nar hon sedan blir kidnappad tappar Creasy allt forstånd. Han ger sig ut på en vansinnesjakt for att finna henne och ingenting kan stoppa honom.

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Once Were Warriors
programme.desc: Hos familjen Heke finns ingen frid att tala om. Jake Heke blir våldsam nar han dricker, den ena sonen har gått med i ett gatugang och den andra står infor åtal. Mamman Beth och barnen står infor det svåra, men livsavgorande valet mellan att stanna kvar i en hopplos situation, och att slå sig fria. Once Were Warriors ar ett prisvinnande familjedrama om att bejaka sitt forflutna for att skapa sin framtid.

programme.title: Frozen River
programme.desc: Dagarna fore julafton på gransen mellan USA och Kanada, tvingas Ray Eddy ta saken i egna hander nar hennes man forsvinner med handpenningen till nya husvagnen. Hon finner motvilligt en ovantad kumpan i urinvånaren Lila Littlewolf, som forsorjer sig på att smuggla illegala invandrare over gransen. Frozen River ar ett kargt kriminaldrama som vann Grand Jury Prize nar den hade premiar på Sundance filmfestival 2008. Filmen nominerades aven till två Oscars.

En dag råkar han på Lucy, en sot butiksexpedit for en underkladesaffar och livet tycks antligen ta en positiv vandning. Tillsammans tar de sig an att bygga upp Bills dåliga sjalvfortroende!

programme.title: 10 Items or Less
programme.desc: Oscar och Golden Globevinnaren Morgan Freeman spelar har en filmstjarna som ger sig ut på rollforberedande research i ett snabbkop i ostra Los Angeles. Han moter en snabbtalande kassorska (Paz Vega) och de ger sig av på en gemensam resa for att visa varandra sina respektive varldar. Strandad utan vare sig mobiltelefon eller bil accepterar han tjejens erbjudande om att ge honom lift tillbaka till Beverly Hills. Under resans gång upptacker emellertid det har till synes omaka paret att de har vissa gemensamma namnare som for all framtid kommer att forandra deras syn på deras egna liv...

programme.title: Mama Weed
programme.desc: Nar en underbetald polistolk under ett tillslag upptacker att en av de involverade ar en person i hennes narhet tar hon ett livsavgorande beslut. Hon lyckas beslagta den massiva mangden hasch både polisen och den undre varlden vill åt, och med hennes erfarenheter i faltet och polisens resurser borjar hon sin egna kriminella verksamhet och sadlar om till knarklangare.

programme.title: Mångalen (Moonstruck)
programme.desc: I denna klassiska romantiska komedi ar en anka från Brooklyn (Cher) redo att gifta om sig. Den har gången planerar hon att gora det ratt, aven om hon måste saga ”ja” till en man hon egentligen inte alskar. Men nar hon blir kar i sin fastmans bror (Nicolas Cage) foljer en romantisk komplikation vardig de storsta komiska operorna! Olympia Dukakis medverkar också.

programme.title: The Happytime Murders
programme.desc: I en varld dar "puppets" lever bland manniskor, men inte riktigt har uppnåt samma status, jobbar detektiv Phil (spelad av Bill Barretta). Han återforenas med sin forna partner, detektiv Connie Edwards (Melissa McCarthy) for att hitta den som mordade detektiv Phils bror och som nu ar ute efter flera ur casten till 80-talets succe-TV-serie The Happytime Gang. Phils gamla tjej (spelad av Elisabeth Banks) har utsatts for hot och ar nasta tilltankta offer. Snart pekar misstankarna mot Phil sjalv. Han sticker och måste nu ensam forsoka losa The happytime murders.

programme.title: Adult Life Skills
programme.desc: Anna har fastnat. Snart 30 men bor i sin mammas tradgårdsskjul, pratar knappt med någon, och agnar sin tid åt att gora kortfilmer med sina tummar som skådespelare. Något saknas, och det visar sig att Annas avskildhet ar hennes satt att hantera den stora sorg hon bar på. Men nar hon råkar bli kompis med en åttaårig cowboy borjar hon så sakteliga oppna upp sig... Adult Life Skills ar Rachel Tunnards forsta långfilm och berattar en lika delar sorglig och rolig berattelse om doden och att tvingas leva med den. Broadchurch-stjarnan Jodie Whittaker spelar den tillslutna Anna i en lika humoristisk som vacker rollgestaltning.

programme.title: The Beach Bum
programme.desc: I The Beach Bum får vi folja Moondogs (Matthew McConaughey) skandallosa missoden. En rebellisk och utbrand man som lever livet efter sina egna regler. I rollistan ser vi stjarnor som Snoop Dogg, Isla Fisher, Zac Efron, Jimmy Buffet, Martin Lawrence och Jonah Hill. The Beach Bum ar en ny, originell och revolutionerande komedi av manusforfattaren och regissoren Harmony Korine.

programme.title: Nurse Betty
programme.desc: Betty missar aldrig ett avsnitt av sin favoritsåpa A Reason to Love. Efter ett omvalvande mote med två mordare nar hon ser ett avsnitt forvandlas Betty till Syster Betty och ger sig ut på ett uppdrag for att hitta sin stora karlek doktor David Ravell. Folj Betty på hennes vilda och hysteriska resa over landet i sokandet efter hennes dromprins. Men kan Betty hitta honom innan mordaren hittar henne?

programme.title: Neighbor for sale
programme.desc: Nick (WILL FERRELL) har en riktigt dålig dag. Forst får han sparken från jobbet som han haft i 16 år. Nar han kommer hem upptacker han sedan att hans fru har kastat ut hans saker på grasmattan, och bytt lås i dorren. Han har forlorat allt. Detta får Nick att overge sin sex månader långa nykterhet och med olen i handen inratta sitt vardagsrum på grasmattan, dar han fordriver tiden med att titta på grannarna. Nar polisen dyker upp for att mota bort honom, hittar han losningen i ett kryphål i lagen: invånarna i Plano i Texas har ratt att hålla privata loppmarknader i fem dagar i strack.

programme.title: Wheres The Money
programme.desc: Del ar en snabbtankt ung man från sodra Los Angeles gator. Han får veta att hans pappa, som fortfarande sitter i fangelse, och hans farbror, som precis slappts ut ur fangelse, stal en miljon dollar och gomde det i kallaren till ett gammalt ungkarlshotell. Det ar bara ett problem: En stort universitet håller till i grannskapet och det gamla ungkarlshotellet ar numera ett tillhåll for en studentforening (som ar endast for vita).

programme.title: Pete Smalls Is Dead
programme.desc: En hollywoodregissor har dott. Hans van KC anar ugglor i mossen och beger sig bakom kulisserna for att ta reda på mer, men hur luskar man reda på sanningen i en stad som forsorjer sig på logner?

programme.title: The Trail Beyond
programme.desc: Rod Drew (John Wayne) is in search of a missing miner and his daughter in this Lone Star Picture. Along the way, Drew rescues his pal Wabbi (Noah Beery Jr.) from card cheats who have framed him for murder. Youll find plenty of action and suspense in this vintage horse opera, originally distributed by the kings of the B western, Monogram Pictures!

programme.title: American Empire
programme.desc: This epic of Americas westward march stars Leo Carrillo and Preston Foster in a tale of men building a cattle empire, only to battle rustlers, the weather, and each other! The romantic adventure from director William C. McGann (In Old California, Alcatraz Island) features a strong leading performance by Oscar nominated RKO star Richard Dix (Cimarron, The Ghost Ship) plus cinematography by six-time Oscar nominee Russell Harlan (To Kill a Mockingbird, Rio Bravo).

programme.title: Riders of the Deadline
programme.desc: The 50th of 66 Hopalong Cassidy films finds Hoppy in a vengeful mood. When his good friend Tim Mason is unjustly sent to jail and then killed when trying to escape, Hoppys bitterness gets him drummed out of the Texas Rangers. With the help of his pals California Carson and Jimmy Rogers, he sets out to expose the real culprits and clear Tims name. The usual cast is here, including William Boyd as Hoppy, plus Andy Clyde, Jimmy Rogers, and in one of his earliest roles, Robert Mitchum.

programme.title: Raiders of Red Gap
programme.desc: Bobs Playin A Mystery Hand... Hes Marked For Death By Killer Bullets As Gunfire Echoes Over The Plains! After one of his ranch hands is killed when a gang attacks his ranch, Jim Roberts joins forces with his neighbor in an effort to fight off the Bennett Cattle Co., a company looking to rob them of their land. Things get increasingly dangerous as the company hires Butch Crane, a professional killer, to stop them. Directed by Sam Newfield (Racing Luck (1935), Go-Get-Em, Haines (1936)), Raiders of Red Gap stars Robert Livingston (The Three Mesquiteers (1936), Larceny on the Air (1937)) as Rocky (Lone Rider) Cameron and Al St. John (Billy the Kid Trapped (1942), Border Feud (1947)) as...

programme.title: The Fighting Redhead
programme.desc: When a rustler named Faro kills one of his own henchmen and blames it on Sheila OConner, Red and Little Beaver set out to clear Sheila and to find evidence against Faro and his gang.

programme.title: The Gunman from Bodie
programme.desc: The Rough Riders, a popular group that thrilled audiences in the early 1940s, are after a gang of rustlers in this B-western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Starring Buck Jones, Tim McCoy, and Raymond Hatton, this movie features everything from lawmen going undercover to the Rough Riders looking after an orphaned baby! Also, be on the lookout for the beautiful Christine McIntyre, who would go on to appear in several of the Three Stooges shorts for Colombia Pictures.

programme.title: The Red Rope
programme.desc: Hired killers and Old West outlaws stand front and center in this riveting tale from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Bob Steele, one of the busiest stars in movie history (everything from the silent era to Republic Pictures to working with Clint Eastwood in Hang Em High) is here as Tom Shaw, the target of a bad mans desperation and hate. Steele appeared in more than 240 movies and television shows, but was never more impressive than in The Red Rope!

programme.title: Springtime in the Sierras
programme.desc: Ads for this Roy Rogers classic roared HEAD FOR THE MUSICAL HILLS...ROY IS GUNNIN FOR THRILLS! And thrills are what youll get when you watch this fun, action packed B-Western from Republic Pictures. Theres some great comic relief from Andy Devine and Chester Conklin, two of Hollywoods all-time greats. This old-fashioned shoot-em-up was directed by William Witney, who would go on to direct many of televisions top western sagas, including Bonanza, Wagon Train, and The Wild, Wild West.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney are ordered to San Pablo, Mexico, to find out whats behind the trouble an American tungsten mine is having. When they arrive, they discover the mine has been closed, the wells are all poisoned and the town is in the grip of a malaria epidemic. To make matters worse, the lawmen have been followed by four gunslingers determined to give the American troubleshooters all the trouble they can handle - and more. Russell Hayden stars.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In this episode, Pat and Stoney tangle with a gang of robbers who have hijacked an Army payroll. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan. Originally aired on NBC.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detective Frankie is shot during a robbery. programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, an outlaw gang plans to take over the town by getting Judge Bean to resign over false charges of misconduct. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this epsiode, Storts and Hurley are holding hostage a doll that brings good luck to a Mexican village. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Diablo is in danger when a gang of hired killers comes to town. Lofty finds himself conflicted as he is reluctant to take on the gang once he discovers the leader rescued him back in their days in the U.S. Cavalry. With the state senator possibly the target of the gang, the townspeople call for Lofty to resign amid his reluctance. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primtetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Dave Morgan, an honest lawyer, faces off with Carter Holmes, a crooked politician, in a fiery election campaign. Things take a turn for the worse when Holmes attempts to have his opponent killed. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye learns that his brother has joined the British army and is now a redcoat. However, when he is murdered by a treacherous Indian companion, Hawkeye seeks revenge. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook come across a group of settlers trapped in the Hurons territory.Hawkeye: John Hart. programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben and Adam are in jail, about to be hung for a crime they didnt commit. Joe and Hoss must find out why the witnesses to the alleged crime have lied about what happened before the execution takes place. They receive help from a vagrant named Lassiter who is looking for the men who committed a lynching in Kansas years ago.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bells of San Angelo
programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Dale Evans team up in this tale of silver mines, kidnappings, and secret passages. Roy plays a border guard who has to rescue Dale from the clutches of underhanded miner Rex Gridley (John McGuire). How does he do it? With help from Trigger, of course! With a cast that inclues Andy Devine as Sheriff Cookie Bullfincer, director William Witney gives us an enjoyable drama from the golden era of Republic Pictures!

programme.title: Colorado Sundown
programme.desc: Murder among ranchers is the subject of this Republic Pictures drama. Starring such names as Rex Allen, Slim Pickins, and Chester Clute, this feature was directed by William Whitney. For Trivia Buffs: At one time Whitney was known as the youngest director in Hollywood, having been hired by the newly formed Republic Pictures at the tender age of 21.

programme.title: Captain Apache (Edited Version)
programme.desc: After Harry T. Collier, a beloved commissioner of Indian Affairs, is murdered in late March during the1880s, Captain Apache, an Indian graduate of West Point, is assigned by the army to investigate the crime. Suspecting that O.J., the sheriff of a town bordering the reservation may be involved in the killing, Apache travels there and finds the sheriff dining with his mistress Maude at the Paradise Saloon. Before Apache can question him, however, O.J. abruptly departs and rides out of town with Apache in pursuit. When Apache apprehends him, O.J. swears that he did not kill Collier and relates that the agents dying words were April Morning. Meanwhile, Griffin, a wealthy landowner and six of...

programme.title: The Hanged Man
programme.desc: After a condemned gunfighter (Steve Forrest) survives his own hanging, he helps a young widow stop a pitiless land baron from taking her ranch. This television feature boasts a strong cast of recognizable characters, including Will Geer, Sharon Acker, Dean Jagger, BarBara Luna, and Cameron Mitchell. Director Michael Caffey would go on to work on such hit shows as Barnaby Jones and MacGyver. Also, look for John Mitchum, younger brother of Robert, in a small role. This movie originally aired on ABC-TV and was considered the pilot for a possible series. Writer/producer Andrew Fenady was behind several opular TV shows such as Branded and The Rebel, as well as the 1970 John Wayne feature, Chisum.

programme.title: Winds of the Wasteland
programme.desc: John Wayne stars in this Republic Pictures western about the final days of the Pony Express. Former rider John Blair (Wayne) enters a coach race to win a $25,000 government mail contract, but there are dozens of obstacles in his path. The rest of the cast includes Lane Chandler and Phyllis Fraser, plus Lew Kelly (Lady of Burlesque) doing a great comic turn as Rocky OBrien, the eccentric, self-proclaimed mayor of a deserted mining town.

programme.title: One-Eyed Jacks
programme.desc: Dad Longworth robs a Mexican bank, takes the loot, and leaves his partner Rio to be captured. However, Rio escapes capture and searches for Dad in California.

programme.title: Land of Hunted Men
programme.desc: A band of outlaws is terrorizing a town in the West. Leave it to Ray Crash Corrigan and his Range Busters to ride in and save the day. This film marked the return of Corrigan to the famous series; he had appeared in the first sixteen movies but left for a brief hiatus following 1942s ARIZONA STAGECOACH. This was the 21st of 24 movies in the Range Busters series. Produced between 1940-1943, the Range Busters were a huge financial success for Monogram Pictures.

programme.title: The Terror of Tiny Town
programme.desc: Some incredibly small actors were hired to star in this peculiar cult film. Its all about the villainous Bat Haines (Little Billy Rhodes), who is wreaking havoc on Tiny Town. Can Buck Lawson (Billy Curtis) and the townspeople band together and drive him away? This oddity, which was originally distributed by Columbia Pictures, was directed by one of the most prolific low budget filmmakers in Hollywood history, Sam Newfield, a man with over 200 movies to his credit. While it has appeared on many Worst of all time lists, it deserves to be seen at least once!

programme.title: Young Bill Hickock
programme.desc: Roy Rogers stars as the title character in this actionpacked feature from Republic Pictures. Starring Sally Payne as Calamity Jane, and Rogerss ongoing sidekick George Gabby Hayes, this twofisted saga relives some of Americas most colorful days, and also has time for a few musical numbers, including Up and Down the Prairie, and When the Shadows Fall Across the Rockies.

programme.title: Sitting Bull
programme.desc: A cavalry officer sympathetic to the wronged Sioux tribe fixes a meeting between Chief Sitting Bull and President Grant but a dishonest Indian Agent and a hateful General Custer test the Siouxs patience, threatening to derail the peace-talks. Directed and co-written by Sidney Salkow; starring Dale Robertson, Mary Murphy, J. Carrol Naish. Also, look for legendary character actor Iron Eyes Cody as Crazy Horse.

programme.title: Neath Canadian Skies
programme.desc: Its the mounties versus claim jumpers in this drama from Golden Gate Pictures. Based on an action-packed novel by James Oliver Curwood and directed by B. Reeves Maynard (Undersea Kingdom, The Phantom Empire), the film features an outstanding cast of Poverty Row regulars, including Russell Hayden, Inez Cooper, Cliff Nazarro, I. Stanford Jolley, and Kermit Maynard. For movie buffs: Cinematographer Marcel Le Picard began his career in the silent era and finished with exactly 200 credits!

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men

programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Trigger star in this Republic Pictures feature about the hunt for silver in a deserted ghost town. Songs include Colorado Joe and Everythings Going My Way. Plus, look for Andy Devine as Cookie Bullfincher. Film buffs should look for silent screen foil James Finlayson, a familiar face from various Keystone Cop comedies, as the local sheriff.

programme.title: Im From Arkansas
programme.desc: Welcome to Pitchfork, Arkansas, where proud farmer Juniper Jenkins is celebrating his prize hog Esmeralda giving birth to 18 piglets. The event attracts many tourists and real life country musicians to Pitchfork, including Mary Ford, Merle Travis, Jimmy Wakely, and countless others. How the smalltown folks react to all of the hubbub is a formula for comedy. Starring as Farmer Jenkins is Slim Summerville, a former Keystone Cop who became one of Hollywoods most reliable journeyman, appearing in everything from Charlie Chan and Shirley Temple movies, to the classic All Quiet on the Western Front. Also starring Bruce Bennett Maude Eburne, Cliff Nazarro, Al St. John, Arthur Q. Bryan, and...

programme.title: Heartland
programme.desc: A widow with a young daughter travels to a ranch in Wyoming to manage the household of a rancher. After a while the man and woman develop a relationship that leads to a marriage. But life in the harsh place takes its toll.

programme.title: Mohawk
programme.desc: Kurt Neumann (The Fly, Rocketship X-M) directed this bawdy tale of a love that was louder than war drums! With a cast that includes Scott Brady, Rita Gam, and Neville Brand, the story takes place on a remote army post where an artist romances a trio of women, just as a vengeful settler turns the army and the local Iroquois tribe against each other. Film buffs might like to know that the cinematography for this feature is by four-time Oscar nominee Karl Struss, who won an Academy Award in 1929 for his work on Sunrise.

programme.title: Man from Utah
programme.desc: WHIRLING ROPES AND SNARLING GUNS IN THE GALLOPING GRIP OF A GLAMOROUS DRAMA! John Wayne stars as John Weston, a man hired to investigate shady doings at a local rodeo. It seems all the riders who are on the verge of winning end up dead. Along with Wayne, this tale of action on the range also stars the usual Lone Star Picture stock company, including Gabby Hayes and Yakima Canutt!

programme.title: Fighting Caravans
programme.desc: Clint Belmet (Gary Cooper) is a frontier scout with his hands full in this 1931 Paramount Pictures version of Zane Greys novel. Hes helping guide a wagon train across the country, fighting off various attacks on the way, and falling for his lovely Felice (Lily Damita). Belmets grizzled companions think he should leave the woman alone, but it gets lonely out on the trail, and Felices charms are hard to resist. Featuring such notable character actors of the period as Ernest Torrence, Tully Marshall, and Fred Kolher, this vintage Hollywood Western still packs a wallop!

programme.title: Raiders of Old California
programme.desc: The end of the Mexican-American War finds a brazen U.S. Calvary captain and his men taking over a Spanish land grant. Albert C. Gannaway (The Badge of Marshall Brennan) directs an all-star cast including Jim Davis (Jock Ewing of Dallas), Arleen Whelan (Young Mr. Lincoln) and Lee Van Cleef (The Good, The Bad, and the Ugly). Also, look for appearances by legendary country and western stars Marty Robbins and Faron Young.
